Package back.calculator.types

Class RealValue

java.lang.Object
back.calculator.types.AbstractValue
back.calculator.types.RealValue
public class RealValue extends AbstractValue
Represents a real number. It extends AbstractValue. It uses BigDecimal to store the value.
